[Student "S"]
{NORTH thinks there might be slam if SOUTH holds both minor Aces, so he tries Blackwood.

When SOUTH shows just one Ace NORTH is afraid he will have a trump loser as well, so 
he stops at 5\H.

It turns out that NORTH might make twelve tricks, depending on the \HK situation.}

